description:
Its the final entry in the most forgettable superhero trilogy of all time. But is Venom 3 nothing but another mediocre piece of superhero sludge, or is there a little more entertainment to be found here? Join me for my review.

title: Venom: The Last Dance - A Movie Of All Time
